# Supabase Migrations

1. Name: `NNN_description.sql` (sequential, zero-padded).
2. One concern per migration when possible.
3. Enable RLS: `ALTER TABLE x ENABLE ROW LEVEL SECURITY;` + policies in same file.
4. Use `000_audit_standard.sql` helpers for audit triggers.
5. Add indexes for `(brand_id, status)`, foreign keys.
6. Apply to cloud: `supabase db push` (linked project; no Docker).
7. Update `docs/database/table-dictionary.md` for new tables.

Never edit applied migrations in production — add a new migration instead.
